    <title>记录一次博客搭建过程</title>
    <url>/p/2259.html</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>之前都是在CSDN上写博客，如今发现了hexo这个静态博客，可以部署在GitHub和码云(Gitee)上，就花费了点时间，搭建了一下这个博客，所以记录一下，以及走过的弯路。</p>
<span id="more"></span>
<h2 id="一、前言"><a class="header-anchor" href="#一、前言">¶</a>一、前言</h2>
<p>该博客用的是<a href="https://links.jianshu.com/go?to=https%3A%2F%2Fhexo.io%2Fzh-cn%2Fdocs%2Findex.html">Hexo</a>框架，基于Node.js，搭建博客首先需要有一个GitHub账号并且配置了SSH Keys），然后在GitHub里创建一个名为username.github.io的仓库，还需要本地电脑安装Git、安装Node.js、安装Hexo，这里就不做介绍了，网上教程很多。</p>
<h2 id="二、基础配置"><a class="header-anchor" href="#二、基础配置">¶</a>二、基础配置</h2>
<p>打开你自己hexo博客下的<code>_config.yml</code>文件,修改几个关键信息，然后保存，注：冒号后需要有空格，不需要加引号。</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">title:</span> <span class="string">CangXun233</span> <span class="string">Notes</span>  <span class="string">//你博客的名字</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">subtitle:</span> <span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;</span>  <span class="string">//SEO</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">description:</span> <span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;</span>  <span class="string">//SEO</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">keywords:</span> <span class="string">//SEO</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">author:</span> <span class="string">CangXun</span>  <span class="string">//你的名字</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">language:</span> <span class="string">zh-CN</span>  <span class="string">//语言，这里最好是先不填，然后根据你后续安装主题内的languages文件夹下的名称进行更改</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">timezone:</span>  <span class="string">//时区，为空则从读取本地一，一般不用填写</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="三、主题安装"><a class="header-anchor" href="#三、主题安装">¶</a>三、主题安装</h2>
<p>博客内会有个<code>themes</code>文件夹，其中存放的是主题，默认存放的是<code>landscape</code>主题，如果不喜欢可以去官网的<a href="https://hexo.io/themes/">主题商店</a>中下载其他的主题放到这个文件夹下。</p>
<p>我这边使用的则是比较简单的<strong>NexT</strong>主题,是目前比较火热的主题，安装过程比较简单。</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>安装NexT主题：</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ <span class="built_in">cd</span> myblog        //进入到你自己hexo博客的文件夹下</span><br><span class="line">$ git <span class="built_in">clone</span> https://github.com/iissnan/hexo-theme-next themes/next</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li>
<p>启用NexT主题：<br>
打开博客下的<code>_config.yml</code>文件，找到<code>theme</code>字段将其值更改为<code>next</code></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>验证主题：</p>
<p><strong>注意：每次切换主题之后、验证主题之前都要清除 Hexo 的缓存</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo clean    //清除缓存</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>启动Hexo本地服务器</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>然后你将会看到终端输出</p>
<figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">INFO  Hexo is running at http://localhost:4000/. Press Ctrl+C to stop.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>这行的意思是说你用浏览器打开 <a href="https://links.jianshu.com/go?to=http%3A%2F%2Flocalhost%3A4000">http://localhost:4000</a> 便可看到你的博客了，这只是本地的测试，如果测试没问题就执行Ctrl+C退出去，此时该地址就不能访问了。</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p>OK，现在，你已经成功安装并启用了 NexT 主题。接下来就是对该主题的一些设置。</p>
<h2 id="四、主题配置"><a class="header-anchor" href="#四、主题配置">¶</a>四、主题配置</h2>
<h3 id="1、主题样式选择"><a class="header-anchor" href="#1、主题样式选择">¶</a>1、主题样式选择</h3>
<p><img src="https://xutaiyuan-1255898059.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/blog/image-20220322181248093.png" alt="Pisces样式"></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>NexT主题内置了四种风格，可供我们选择，打开安装完成的<code>Themes/next</code>文件夹下的<code>_config.yml</code>文件，找到<code>Scheme Settings</code></p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Schemes</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># scheme: Muse</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># scheme: Mist</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">scheme:</span> <span class="string">Pisces</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># scheme: Gemini</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li>
<p>我这里选择的是双栏风格的<code>Pisces</code>,你们可以选择自己喜欢的风格。</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="2、头像修改"><a class="header-anchor" href="#2、头像修改">¶</a>2、头像修改</h3>
<p><img src="https://xutaiyuan-1255898059.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/blog/image-20220322181230625.png" alt="头像修改"></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>找到<code>Sidebar Avatar</code>字段</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Sidebar Avatar</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">avatar:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">url:</span> <span class="string">/images/header.jpeg</span>  <span class="comment">#头像地址</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">rounded:</span> <span class="literal">false</span>  <span class="comment">#圆角</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">rotated:</span> <span class="literal">false</span>  <span class="comment">#鼠标悬浮动画 旋转</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="3、添加分类"><a class="header-anchor" href="#3、添加分类">¶</a>3、添加分类</h3>
<ul>
<li>
<p>新建一个categories页面</p>
<figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo new page categories</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li>
<p>你会发现你的<code>source</code>文件夹下有了<code>categorcies/index.md</code></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>打开<code>index.md</code>文件将title设置为<code>title: 分类</code></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>打开 <strong>主题配置文件</strong> 找到<code>menu</code>，将categorcies取消注释</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>把文章归入分类只需在文章的顶部标题下方添加<code>categories</code>字段，即可自动创建分类名并加入对应的分类中</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>例如：</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">title:</span> <span class="string">分类测试文章标题</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">categories:</span> <span class="string">分类名</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="4、添加标签"><a class="header-anchor" href="#4、添加标签">¶</a>4、添加标签</h3>
<ul>
<li>
<p>新建一个标签页面</p>
<figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo new page tags</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li>
<p>你会发现你的<code>source</code>文件夹下有了<code>tags/index.md</code>，打开<code>index.md</code>文件将title设置为<code>title: 标签</code></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>打开 <strong>主题配置文件</strong> 找到<code>menu</code>，将tags取消注释</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>把文章添加标签只需在文章的顶部标题下方添加<code>tags</code>字段，即可自动创建标签名并归入对应的标签中</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>例如：</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">title:</span> <span class="string">标签测试文章标题</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">tags:</span> </span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">标签1</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">标签2</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">...</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="5、添加关于页面"><a class="header-anchor" href="#5、添加关于页面">¶</a>5、添加关于页面</h3>
<ul>
<li>
<p>新建一个关于页面</p>
<figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo new page about</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li>
<p>你会发现你的<code>source</code>文件夹下有了<code>about/index.md</code>，打开<code>index.md</code>文件即可编辑关于你的信息，可以随便编辑。</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>打开 <strong>主题配置文件</strong> 找到<code>menu</code>，将about取消注释</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="6、添加阅读全文按钮"><a class="header-anchor" href="#6、添加阅读全文按钮">¶</a>6、添加阅读全文按钮</h3>
<p><img src="https://xutaiyuan-1255898059.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/blog/image-20220322181209807.png" alt="阅读全文按钮"></p>
<p>因为在你的博客主页会有多篇文章，如果你想让你的文章只显示一部分，多余的可以点击阅读全文来查看，那么你需要在你的文章中添加：</p>
<figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">&lt;!--more--&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>其后面的部分就不会显示了，只能点击阅读全文才能看</p>
<h3 id="7、设置网站缩略图标"><a class="header-anchor" href="#7、设置网站缩略图标">¶</a>7、设置网站缩略图标</h3>
<ul>
<li>
<p>先将图片转换为16x16和32x32两个格式，并放在<code>themes/next/source/images</code>文件夹中，然后打开<strong>主题配置文件</strong>找到<code>favicon</code>，将<code>small、medium、apple_touch_icon</code>三个字段的值都设置成<code>/images/图片名.jpg</code>就可以了，其他字段都注释掉。</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>例如：</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">favicon:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">small:</span> <span class="string">/images/favicon-16x16.ico</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">medium:</span> <span class="string">/images/favicon-32x32.ico</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">apple_touch_icon:</span> <span class="string">/images/header.jpeg</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="8、设置侧边栏社交账户展示"><a class="header-anchor" href="#8、设置侧边栏社交账户展示">¶</a>8、设置侧边栏社交账户展示</h3>
<p><img src="https://xutaiyuan-1255898059.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/blog/image-20220322181156031.png" alt="侧边栏社交账户"></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>打开 <strong>主题配置文件</strong> 找到<code>Social Links</code>，将你需要展示的社交账户取消注释，并添加对应的链接即可，也可以直接添加。</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>例如：</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">social:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">GitHub:</span> <span class="string">https://github.com/cangxun233</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">fab</span> <span class="string">fa-github</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">E-Mail:</span> <span class="string">mailto:49234737@qq.com</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">fa</span> <span class="string">fa-envelope</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="9、添加站点访问计数"><a class="header-anchor" href="#9、添加站点访问计数">¶</a>9、添加站点访问计数</h3>
<p><img src="https://xutaiyuan-1255898059.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/blog/image-20220322181137657.png" alt="访问计数"></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>打开 <strong>主题配置文件</strong> 找到<code>busuanzi_count</code>，将<code>enable</code>改为true，其他默认即可。</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">busuanzi_count:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">total_visitors:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">total_visitors_icon:</span> <span class="string">fa</span> <span class="string">fa-user</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">total_views:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">total_views_icon:</span> <span class="string">fa</span> <span class="string">fa-eye</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">post_views:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">post_views_icon:</span> <span class="string">fa</span> <span class="string">fa-eye</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="10、去掉文章目录自动编号"><a class="header-anchor" href="#10、去掉文章目录自动编号">¶</a>10、去掉文章目录自动编号</h3>
<p><img src="https://xutaiyuan-1255898059.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/blog/image-20220322181108187.png" alt="去掉自动编号"></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>打开<strong>主题配置文件</strong>，找到<code>toc</code>,将<code>number</code>改为<code>false</code>即可</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>例如：</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">toc:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">number:</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">wrap:</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">expand_all:</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">max_depth:</span> <span class="number">6</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="11、添加版权信息"><a class="header-anchor" href="#11、添加版权信息">¶</a>11、添加版权信息</h3>
<p><img src="https://xutaiyuan-1255898059.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/blog/image-20220322181046530.png" alt="版权声明"></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>要想开启博客的版权功能，需要设置<strong>主题配置文件</strong>：</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">creative_commons:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">license:</span> <span class="string">by-nc-sa</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">sidebar:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">post:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="12、添加右上角GitHub-Banner"><a class="header-anchor" href="#12、添加右上角GitHub-Banner">¶</a>12、添加右上角GitHub Banner</h3>
<p><img src="https://xutaiyuan-1255898059.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/blog/image-20220322181526984.png" alt="GitHub banner"></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>想要给博客添加一个banner，需要修改<strong>主题配置文件</strong>：</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">github_banner:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">permalink:</span> <span class="string">https://github.com/cangxun233</span>  <span class="string">//改成自己GitHub的地址</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">title:</span> <span class="string">Follow</span> <span class="string">me</span> <span class="string">on</span> <span class="string">GitHub</span>  <span class="string">//悬浮文字</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="13、添加右下角文章进度以及返回顶部按钮"><a class="header-anchor" href="#13、添加右下角文章进度以及返回顶部按钮">¶</a>13、添加右下角文章进度以及返回顶部按钮</h3>
<p><img src="https://xutaiyuan-1255898059.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/blog/image-20220322181806580.png" alt="返回顶部按钮"></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>修改<strong>主题配置文件</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">back2top:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">sidebar:</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">scrollpercent:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="五、写作"><a class="header-anchor" href="#五、写作">¶</a>五、写作</h2>
<p>以上所有的工作都完成了，并设置了一套你自己喜欢的主题样式，接下来就可以写博客了。</p>
<h3 id="1、新建一篇文章"><a class="header-anchor" href="#1、新建一篇文章">¶</a>1、新建一篇文章</h3>
<ul>
<li>
<p>layout：模板，如果不写将使用默认模板，一般不写，直接<code>$ hexo new title</code></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>title：文章标题，如果标题包含空格的话，请使用引号括起来。</p>
<figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo new layout title</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ul>
<p>新建的文章将会存在<code>username/source/_posts</code>中，<code>_posts</code>就是默认模板，文章文件名称将会是<code>title.md</code>，接下来就可以打开该文件进行编辑写你的文章了。</p>
<h3 id="2、生成静态文件"><a class="header-anchor" href="#2、生成静态文件">¶</a>2、生成静态文件</h3>
<ul>
<li>
<p>写完文章之后执行，来生成静态网页文件</p>
<figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo g        //hexo generate的缩写</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="3、启动本地服务器"><a class="header-anchor" href="#3、启动本地服务器">¶</a>3、启动本地服务器</h3>
<ul>
<li>
<p>输入：</p>
<figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo s        //hexo server的缩写</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ul>
<p>本地服务器启动完之后就如同上面验证主题一样，访问 <a href="https://links.jianshu.com/go?to=http%3A%2F%2Flocalhost%3A4000">http://localhost:4000</a> 来验证一下你写的文章预览效果。</p>
<h3 id="4、部署网站"><a class="header-anchor" href="#4、部署网站">¶</a>4、部署网站</h3>
<ul>
<li>
<p>安装部署工具</p>
<figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li>
<p>安装完毕后打开博客目录下的<code>_config.yml</code>文件，翻到最底部找到deploy节点编辑链接</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>例如：</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">deploy:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">type:</span> <span class="string">git</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">repository:</span> <span class="string">https://github.com/YoungerLi/youngerli.github.io.git</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">branch:</span> <span class="string">master</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li>
<p>其中<code>https://github.com/YoungerLi/youngerli.github.io.git</code>就是你GitHub中创建的仓库地址，在这复制即可</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>最后，上传并部署网站</p>
<figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo d        //hexo deploy的缩写</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>以后每次写完文章之后依次执行以下命令就可以发布更新了</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo clean      // 清除缓存</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo g          // 生成静态网页文件</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo d          // 将本地博客发布到github</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li>
<p>若是闲麻烦，也可以在清单文件<code>package.json</code>中添加script来一键运行多个指令。</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>例如：</p>
<figure class="highlight json"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">&quot;scripts&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="punctuation">&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="attr">&quot;build&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;hexo generate&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="attr">&quot;clean&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;hexo clean&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="attr">&quot;deploy&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;hexo deploy&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="attr">&quot;server&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;hexo server&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="attr">&quot;ok&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span><span class="string">&quot;hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo generate &amp;&amp; hexo deploy&quot;</span> </span><br><span class="line"> <span class="punctuation">&#125;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li>
<p>我这里新加了一行ok 以后只需要运行<code>npm run ok</code>即可一键完成生产加上传操作，最好上传前使用<code>hexo s</code>来查看写好的内容有没有问题，再执行。</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="六、更多"><a class="header-anchor" href="#六、更多">¶</a>六、更多</h2>
